llama.cpp, a C/C++ implementation of LLaMA-based large language 
models that provides state-of-the-art performance on a wide range of 
hardware.

GPU acceleration options 
WITH_CUDA=yes, WITH_HIP=yes, WITH_SYCL=yes, WITH_VULKAN=yes 
WITH_OPENCL=yes. Mathematical library optimization WITH_BLAS=yes 

For OPENCL you also need
export OPENCL_VENDOR_PATH=/etc/OpenCL/vendors/mesa.icd
In my system OpenCL had no benefit.

llama.cpp has releases every hours. Maybe you want to build
the latest release.

Optional requirement: OpenBLAS. (in my system no benefit)
